/**
 * Enables and configures the IBEX constraints solver backend for the
 * refinement process.
 *
 * Activating this theory allows the solver engine to delegate numerical
 * and constraints to the IBEX solver for high-performance reasoning.
 *
 * This solver is activated by default.
 */
#theory ibex.
